  "chapter": "⚙ 安裝 Claude Code",
  "capturedAt": "2026-04-23T18:57:11.311Z",
  "intro": {
    "voiceover": "Claude Code 安裝教學,Mac 版。"
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "ch1-s1",
      "title": "打開終端機（Terminal）",
      "voiceovers": [
        "打開終端機。Finder 進工具程式,或 Launchpad 搜尋 Terminal。"
      ],
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "每一台 Mac 都有內建的**「終端機」**應用程式。有兩個方式:"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "**方法 A：** Finder → 應用程式 → 工具程式 → **終端機**"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "**方法 B：** 用四指往內收打開 **Launchpad**,搜尋 **Terminal** 點開"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "screenshots/tutorial-ch1/01-打開終端機-terminal.png",
          "alt": "在 Launchpad 搜尋 Terminal"
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "kind": "tip",
          "icon": "💡",
          "text": "打開後會看到黑色(或白色)視窗,閃爍游標就是終端機。"
        }
      ],
      "pointAt": null,
      "highlightBox": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ch1-s2",
      "title": "安裝 Claude Code",
      "voiceovers": [
        "貼上安裝指令,按 Enter。等它跑完。",
        "看到 Installation Complete,就代表 Claude Code 安裝成功了。"
      ],
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "在終端機**貼上**下面這行指令,按 **Enter**:"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "text": "curl -fsSL https://claude.ai/install.sh | bash"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "screenshots/tutorial-ch1/02-安裝-claude-code.gif",
          "alt": "在終端機貼上安裝指令"
        },
        {
          "type": "pageBreak"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "等它跑完,看到 **\"Installation Complete\"** 代表安裝成功。"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "screenshots/tutorial-ch1/03-安裝-claude-code-b.png",
          "alt": "Claude Code 安裝完成畫面"
        }
      ],
      "pointAt": null,
      "highlightBox": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ch1-s3",
      "title": "設定環境變數 PATH",
      "voiceovers": [
        "貼上 PATH 指令按 Enter。沒出現紅字就是成功。"
      ],
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "讓你**以後每次打開終端機**都能直接用 `claude` 指令。貼上指令,按 **Enter**:"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "text": "echo 'export PATH=\"$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH\"' >> ~/.zshrc && source ~/.zshrc"
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "kind": "info",
          "icon": "ℹ️",
          "text": "這行指令不會有任何輸出,是正常的。沒有紅色錯誤就代表成功。"
        }
      ],
      "pointAt": null,
      "highlightBox": null
    }
  ]
}
